Substance (symbol: $n$) is a [[id:4d6216d5-3d24-415b-bd06-83a9f9ef7469][standard unit]]. Also referred to as the chemical amount.

The base quantity is a [[id:c69540fc-65d0-4892-a5d5-c690cc92f815][mole]].
